Name:                glew
Version:             0.1.0
Cabal-Version:       >= 1.2
Synopsis:            GLEW mini-binding
Category:            graphics
Description:
  Glew is a Haskell binding to a (currently very small) subset of GLEW
  (<http://glew.sourceforge.net>).
  .
